  <bns:description>Standard GET operation that queries the HR_Departments table in SQL Server to retrieve enrichment data for a new hire. Takes the department_code from Salesforce as a named parameter and returns the full department record including cost center, manager hierarchy, and building location. Demo talking point: "The SQL is clean and readable - a standard SELECT with a named parameter. Boomi substitutes the department code from the Salesforce record at runtime, executes the query, and returns a structured JSON response. Your database team can review and adjust the query directly in Boomi without touching any application code."</bns:description>
